Package: OffensiveToolMapper
Title: Offensive Security Tool Intelligence and MITRE ATT&CK Mapping
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(
        given = "KNikitaaa",
        family = "Maintainer",
        email = "KNikitaaa@users.noreply.github.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
    )
Description: Collects offensive cybersecurity tool data from open sources,
    validates and enriches it with large language models, maps tools to
    MITRE ATT&CK techniques, and exposes the results through analytics,
    Shiny dashboards, and MCP interfaces.
URL: https://KNikitaaa.github.io/CyberSecML-NetAdmins/, https://github.com/KNikitaaa/CyberSecML-NetAdmins
